 VTuber索帕特拉《Anchant Roman》剧分布魅力十足https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-ancient-roman-play-streaming-is-full-of-charm/ https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-ancient-roman-play-streaming-is-full-of-charm/#respondp2y_admin Mon, 10 Jul 2023 16:05:34 +0000 VTuberゲームバーチャルTwitterYouTubeYouTuberからすまアンシャントロマン ~Power of Dark Side~バーチャルYouTuberプレステ個人勢周防パトラ https://p2y.jp/?p=96151 <p> VTuber Suo Patra（独立）从2023年7月1日开始玩游戏软件《Anchant Roman ~Power of Dark Side~》，同才艺的魅力是[…]</p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-ancient-roman-play-streaming-is-full-of-charm/">VTuber Suo Patra 的《Anchant Romain》剧透魅力十足，</a>首发于<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; <p></p><p> VTuber <strong>Suo Patra</strong> （独立）从2023年7月1日开始玩游戏软件《 <strong>Anchant Roman ~Power of Dark Side~</strong> 》，充满了才子的魅力。就是内容。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img data-attachment-id="96202" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-suou-patra-ancient-roman-play-streaming-is-full-of-charm/vtuber_suou_patra_ancient_roman_play_streaming_is_full_of_charm/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_suou_patra_ancient_roman_play_streaming_is_full_of_charm.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_suou_patra_ancient_roman_play_streaming_is_full_of_charm" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_suou_patra_ancient_roman_play_streaming_is_full_of_charm.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_suou_patra_ancient_roman_play_streaming_is_full_of_charm.jpg" decoding="async" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_suou_patra_ancient_roman_play_streaming_is_full_of_charm.jpg" alt="VTuber索帕特拉《Anchant Roman》剧分布魅力十足" class="wp-image-96202" width="435" height="244"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源： <a href="https://twitter.com/Patra_HNST/status/1674718788099674115" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="推特">推特</a></figcaption></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">“罕见的他妈的游戏”Anchant Roman</h3><p> 《Anchant Roman ～Power of Dark Side～》是Nihon System于1998年4月23日（平成10年）发行的PlayStation游戏软件。</p><p>游戏中几乎所有元素都被认为是商业作品，被游戏用户公认为“kusoge”之一，意思<strong>是比以前更糟糕的游戏。Suma先生</strong>称这部作品为“<em>完美操”游戏《一切都结束了</em>》，近年来游戏发行和剪辑视频的发布再次引起人们的关注。我们记录一下价格。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="一场完美的游戏，一切都结束了 [Enchant Roman]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sJVjUf9tjmE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="彻底解说因为太狗屎而成为高价溢价的完美kusoge！第 1 部分 [附魔罗马]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vVLlPwDPRgs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="完美 kusoge Anchant Romain 第 2 部分的完整评论" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RM4H84txN7w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p>然后，你就可以把这部作品当作一个“可爱的操蛋游戏”来欣赏，把它的粗俗元素当作一个故事来欣赏，而开场电影中出现的所谓“无理吹老头”已经成为了一个网络迷因。当今吸引许多人关注的游戏软件，例如在“RTA in Japan”活动中玩的游戏。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="Enchant Romain -Power of Dark Side- - RTA 日本夏季赛 2022 年" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yPd6DJRiGCM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="otvyk64ac4b795b3a0" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
